name: SDO_DAS_ChangeSummary.getChangeType
purpose: Get the type of change made to an SDO_DataObject

return.description:
The type of change which has been made. The change type is expressed as an 
   enumeration and will be one of the following four values:
   
    
     
      SDO_DAS_ChangeSummary::NONESDO_DAS_ChangeSummary::MODIFICATIONSDO_DAS_ChangeSummary::ADDITIONSDO_DAS_ChangeSummary::DELETION
